subscriber by the service provider named in such process or request was supplied to or requested by that governmental authority and the date on which the supplying or request took place;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/5/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/5/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft18%2Fs2705%2Fa%2F5%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"that notification of such customer or subscriber was delayed;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iii","heading":null,"label":"iii","identifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/5/B/iii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/5/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft18%2Fs2705%2Fa%2F5%2FB%2Fiii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"what governmental entity or court made the certification or determination pursuant to which that delay was made; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"iv","heading":null,"label":"iv","identifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/5/B/iv","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/5/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft18%2Fs2705%2Fa%2F5%2FB%2Fiv","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"which provision of this chapter allowed such delay.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t18/s2705/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft18%2Fs2705%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"As used in this subsection, the term “supervisory official” means the investigative agent in charge or assistant investigative agent in 